HEADWORD: Osmiamic
<hw>Os`mi*am"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Osmi</ets>um
+ <ets>am</ets>ido.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>Of, pertaining to, or
